---
title: Crispy Maple Mustard Chicken with Roasted Potato Wedges & Asparagus
description: Some say crispy panko-coated chicken is pretty tough to top. Those people clearly don’t know our chefs. They went and made crispy chicken 25x (a scientific number) more delicious by drizzling it with a lick-your-plate-style maple and mustard sauce. On the side, there’s seasoned potato wedges and crispy-edged roasted carrots. The best part? Everything comes together on one baking sheet in under 40 minutes. Because couldn’t we all use a little more time (and fewer dishes to wash)?

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66b14f1678d91450badf815a-09129e01.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/66b3d43b995e511e4eca9e64-en-US.pdf
